          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/TrueFit_007.jpg",
            "heading": "Protein and fiber, finally together.",
            "text": "<p>Most protein powders digest too quickly, spiking and crashing before your body can fully put it to work. TrueFit combines 25g of grass-fed whey with whole-food fiber to slow digestion, support steadier amino acid delivery, and keep you fuller, longer.</p>"
          }
        },
        "row_AhH43k": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_19_2026_11_17_11_PM.png",
            "heading": "Improve digestion and gut health",
            "text": "<p>Powered by prebiotic fiber and 1 billion CFU probiotics, TrueFit supports a balanced microbiome from the inside out. A happy gut means better nutrient absorption, smoother digestion, and steady, all-day energy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--15510886875181__894e738c-d102-4245-8b24-f42264ccfba5-167805591942128572-2": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/TrueFit_001.jpg",
            "heading": "Simple, effective, delicious weight loss",
            "text": "<p>Real food ingredients keep you satisfied longer, so cravings fade and portion sizes naturally shrink. Replace one meal a day with TrueFit and let whole-food nutrition do the heavy lifting.</p>"
          }
        },
        "4959ee0d-d1fe-4639-92fc-81e688e40b63": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_19_2026_11_11_51_PM.png",
            "heading": "Build and retain lean muscle",
            "text": "<p>Strong muscles mean a longer, healthier, more capable life, period. TrueFit delivers 25g of grass-fed whey per serving, the gold standard for building lean muscle and keeping it as you age.</p>"
          }
        }
